'''Kirl''' was a province on [[Munto Codru/Legends|Munto Codru]]. [[Ambassador/Legends|Ambassador]] [[Kirl (Codru-Ji)|Kirl]] was named after his home province. The [[Codru-Ji]] from Kirl were known as Kirlians.

